com.datapak.shopify_java_api.model

Class BillingAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datapak.shopify_java_api.model.ShopifyObject
      • com.datapak.shopify_java_api.model.BillingAddress

  • public class BillingAddress
extends ShopifyObject
    Represents a BillingAddress The mailing address associated with the payment method. This address is an optional field that will not be be available on orders that do not require one.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    jbrown
